snippet.title: IBUKI Gameplay Teaser (Download link in description)
snippet.description:
Get the game here: https://markli.itch.io/ibuki



IBUKI is a side-scrolling beat 'em up game where you play as a locked-up demon who has to fight her way out in order to escape from a shrine maiden. As a derivative work of ZUN's Touhou Project, the game reveals an untold story about Suika Ibuki's past.


Mark Li (developer): https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC-FScgLaPX8D6c7ZCXZZzuw

                                   https://itch.io/profile/markli
